data.description: This home is situated on a one acre, fully fenced and gated lot and WATERFRONT property. Walk out your backdoor and you're created by a large backyard and the beautiful waterfront cove. Large ceilings in the great room and a loft style bedroom perfect for kids or for guests. Come enjoy this home and the wonderful outdoors! Home is currently a vacation rental so it's also perfect for investors! Schedule your showing today. Room measurements are approximate. Furnishings are available and negotiable.
